chor-text"><img class="publication-cover-image" src="https://ars.els-cdn.com/content/image/1-s2.0-S0014488617X00071-cov150h.gif" alt="Experimental Neurology"/></span></span></a></div></div><div class="PageDivider"></div><h1 id="screen-reader-main-title" class="Head u-font-serif u-h2 u-margin-s-ver"><div class="article-dochead"><span>Review Article</span></div><span class="title-text">Developing a data sharing community for spinal cord injury research</span></h1><div class="Banner" id="banner"><div class="wrapper truncated"><div aria-live="polite"></div><div class="AuthorGroups"><div class="author-group" id="author-group"><span class="sr-only">Author links open overlay panel</span><button class="button-link button-link-secondary button-link-underline" type="button" data-sd-ui-side-panel-opener="true" data-xocs-content-type="author" data-xocs-content-id="au0005" aria-haspopup="dialog"><span class="button-link-text-container"><span class="button-link-text"><span class="react-xocs-alternative-link"><span class="given-name">Alison</span> <span class="text surname">Callahan</span> </span><span class="author-ref" id="baf0005"><sup>a</sup></span><svg focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 102 128" height="20" title="Author email or social media contact details icon" class="icon icon-envelope react-xocs-author-icon u-fill-grey8"><path d="M55.8 57.2c-1.78 1.31-5.14 1.31-6.9 0L17.58 34h69.54L55.8 57.19zM0 32.42l42.94 32.62c2.64 1.95 6.02 2.93 9.4 2.93s6.78-.98 9.42-2.93L102 34.34V24H0zM92 88.9L73.94 66.16l-8.04 5.95L83.28 94H18.74l18.38-23.12-8.04-5.96L10 88.94V51.36L0 42.9V104h102V44.82l-10 8.46V88.9"></path></svg></span></span></button>, <button class="button-link button-link-secondary button-link-underline" type="button" data-sd-ui-side-panel-opener="true" data-xocs-content-type="author" data-xocs-content-id="au0010" aria-haspopup="dialog"><span class="button-link-text-container"><span class="button-link-text"><span class="react-xocs-alternative-link"><span class="given-name">Kim D.</span> <span class="text surname">Anderson</span> </span><span class="author-ref" id="baf0010"><sup>b</sup></span> <span class="author-ref" id="baf0015"><sup>c</sup></span></span></span></button>, <button class="button-link button-link-secondary button-link-underline" type="button" data-sd-ui-side-panel-opener="true" data-xocs-content-type="author" data-xocs-content-id="au0015" aria-haspopup="dialog"><span class="button-link-text-container"><span class="button-link-text"><span class="react-xocs-alternative-link"><span class="given-name">Michael S.</span> <span class="text surname">Beattie</span> </span><span class="author-ref" id="baf0020"><sup>d</sup></span></span></span></button>, <button class="button-link button-link-secondary button-link-underline" type="button" data-sd-ui-side-panel-opener="true" data-xocs-content-type="author" data-xocs-content-id="au0020" aria-haspopup="dialog"><span class="button-link-text-container"><span class="button-link-text"><span class="react-xocs-alternative-link"><span class="given-name">John L.</span> <span class="text surname">Bixby</span> </span><span class="author-ref" id="baf0010"><sup>b</sup></span> <span class="author-ref" id="baf0025"><sup>e</sup></span> <span class="author-ref" id="baf0030"><sup>f</sup></span></span></span></button>, <button class="button-link button-link-secondary button-link-underline" type="button" data-sd-ui-side-panel-opener="true" data-xocs-content-type="author" data-xocs-content-id="au0025" aria-haspopup="dialog"><span class="button-link-text-container"><span class="button-link-text"><span class="react-xocs-alternative-link"><span class="given-name">Adam R.</span> <span class="text surname">Ferguson</span> </span><span class="author-ref" id="baf0020"><sup>d</sup></span> <span class="author-ref" id="baf0035"><sup>g</sup></span></span></span></button>, <button class="button-link button-link-secondary button-link-underline" type="button" data-sd-ui-side-panel-opener="true" data-xocs-content-type="aut